Modified the Company constructor and variables, as well as existing company related commands (EditCompanyCommand, AddCommandParser) to accommodate the new Internship data.

Added support for formatting Companies and Internships by modifying the formatCompany command and introducing the formatInternship command in Messages.java.

Added the DateTimeParserUtil class to parse any given String or LocalDateTime object, provided that the given object is valid.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Description class to Person model with tests
commitResults.messageBody:
- Introduced Description class to enhance the Person model.
- Prepared the foundation to achieve the following:
  * Store all People and Companies in PeopleList and CompaniesList respectively.
  * Maintain a filtered ObservableList<People> for selected People objects (e.g., search results) for UI binding.
  * Maintain a sorted and filtered ObservableList<Companies> for selected Companies, allowing UI to auto-update based on changes.
  * Incorporate a UserPref object to capture user preferences, exposed as ReadOnlyUserPref.
  * Ensure Model remains independent of other components for integrity.

Further refinements will be needed to fully realize the described features.
